

TUWING

   tuwing
   every time,
   every now and then

   tuwing Lunes
   every Monday

   tuwing umaga
   every morning

   tuwing hapon
   every afternoon

   tuwing gabi
   whenever it’s night

   Tuwing nakikita kita…
   Every time I see you…

   Tuwing nakikita kita, nahihiya ako.
   Every time I see you, I feel shy.
